name: Beauty and The Burger
description:
This masterpiece is part of Moxxy’s “She Craves” series. This piece is a limited edition of 250 and comes signed, numbered and personally finished off by the artist with acrylic texture providing a custom, distinctive artistic look. Your work of art comes ready to hang with a sturdy, black backer board and hanging hardware is pre-installed. 

*Ships UPS Ground within 7-14 days.
